ason stages, respectively. Overall, this research provides insights into the assemblage of bat-\u00adassociated bacterial communities and will aid in the development of conservation strategies against fungal disease.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Li, Aoqiang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Li, Zhongle", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Leng, Haixia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jin, Longru", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Xiao, Yanhong", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sun, Keping", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Feng, Jiang", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/5776ae9e6363b966c4eebf8ba54dce5a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/9adff7996889bf4390129511ccecba00ad1f71a305d777fd050a4557df93fcf7", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YKVLIVJT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YKVLIVJT", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/09ddb9cf8a75ed35db9ec5ee662b9069!/b86520-89066", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "16", "pages": "4695-4707", "title": "Molecular Ecology", "volume": "32"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/5776ae9e6363b966c4eebf8ba54dce5a"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:i